1.01.name: wordpress/comment-rating-field-plugin
1.01.description: Comment Rating Field Plugin is a plugin which adds a 5 star rating field to the end of a comment form in WordPress, allowing the site visitor to optionally submit a rating along with their comment. Ratings are displayed as stars below the comment text.
